#: src/features/weather/ui/tile.tsx:124
msgid "March"
msgstr "Mars"

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/day-of-the-dead.tsx:79
msgid "Marigolds, papel picado, sugar skulls, candles, and favourite foods form a visual language of welcome and connection."
msgstr "Les soucis, le papel picado, les crânes en sucre, les bougies et les plats préférés composent un langage visuel d’accueil et de lien."

#: src/features/weather/ui/tile.tsx:126
msgid "May"
msgstr "Mai"

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/autumn-equinox.tsx:133
msgid "Meanwhile, billions of birds are mid-migration, navigating by stars, magnetic fields, and landmarks passed down through generations."
msgstr "Pendant ce temps, des milliards d’oiseaux sont en pleine migration, se guidant par les étoiles, les champs magnétiques et des repères transmis de génération en génération."

#: src/features/weather/ui/tile.tsx:88
msgid "moderate drizzle"
msgstr "bruine modérée"

#: src/features/weather/ui/tile.tsx:93
msgid "moderate rain"
msgstr "pluie modérée"

#: src/features/weather/ui/tile.tsx:102
msgid "moderate rain showers"
msgstr "averses modérées"

#: src/features/weather/ui/tile.tsx:98
