msgid "Traditional stories of the monster Nian are said to have inspired the use of loud sounds, firecrackers, and the colour red as symbols of protection and good fortune."
msgstr "Les histoires traditionnelles du monstre Nian auraient inspiré l’usage de sons forts, de pétards et de la couleur rouge comme symboles de protection et de bonne fortune."

